{"tid":599458,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度男遭火車輾過身體斷兩截 奇蹟生還","createTime":"2018-03-20T12:14:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T13:23:21.000Z","uid":3393,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4f5b2aa238fcf59c8077d5afb15254efa20e04ba","tid":599458,"uid":3393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T12:14:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180319/_2018031912463288887_detail.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180319%2F_2018031912463288887_detail.jpg&d=AViq3vxGpG8D50IWgIFLqDM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=c1b9ffd8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180319%2F_2018031912463288887_detail.jpg&h=1f1dddcc\" target=\"_blank\">http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180319/_2018031912463288887_detail.jpg</a><br />\n男子被火車輾過後上下半身分離，竟能奇蹟存活。 網圖<br />\n<br />\n印度新德里發生一宗駭人意外。一名男子從火車上跌落路軌，結果被後來駛至的另一列火車輾過，身體被「腰斬」斷成上下兩截，該名男子奇蹟地存活，目擊者指，他當時用雙手撐起上半身，向警員說出姓名。男子其後被送院搶救，目前仍在醫院接受治療。<br />\n<br />\n事件發生在印度新德里火車站，據目擊者指，日前一名男子疑失重心摔落路軌，剛巧有另一列火車經過，男子被活生生輾成兩截，上下半身分離，血肉模糊，場面駭人。警員和火車站職員趕到現場，起初發現該名男子趴在路軌上無反應，突然男子雙手移動，用力撐著地挺起上半身，將現場的人嚇倒。據目擊者表示，該男子甚至可以與人對話，意識清楚，期間向警員說出自己的姓名。警方馬上將男子送往就近醫院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，男子在接受手術及術後看護後，健康狀況有所改善，院方表示男子上下半身已無法拼合，院方將致力確保他上半身的器官循環，並會為該名男子提供意外後的心理治療。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/667621-國際-印男遭火車輾過身體斷兩截+奇蹟生還?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F667621-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E5%8D%B0%E7%94%B7%E9%81%AD%E7%81%AB%E8%BB%8A%E8%BC%BE%E9%81%8E%E8%BA%AB%E9%AB%94%E6%96%B7%E5%85%A9%E6%88%AA%2B%E5%A5%87%E8%B9%9F%E7%94%9F%E9%82%84%3F&d=AViq3vxGpG8D50IWgIFLqDM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=6a332d86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F667621-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E5%8D%B0%E7%94%B7%E9%81%AD%E7%81%AB%E8%BB%8A%E8%BC%BE%E9%81%8E%E8%BA%AB%E9%AB%94%E6%96%B7%E5%85%A9%E6%88%AA%2B%E5%A5%87%E8%B9%9F%E7%94%9F%E9%82%84%3F&h=fd41904e\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/667621-國際-印男遭火車輾過身體斷兩截+奇蹟生還?</a>"},{"pid":"b238180eb544bc2912539f249d7996ad68a5e613","tid":599458,"uid":150588,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T12:17:14.000Z","msg":"印度大蛇丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c68388a51ca961290391bfcdf3beae5aed588eb5","tid":599458,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T12:17:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db568e8cb27fdaf978a59a32a62f9c64fe6743c5","tid":599458,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T12:17:54.000Z","msg":"好想睇 戰鬥民族VS印度人"},{"pid":"d56e4b2fae234f52a1b7c9a7f813e634f14647ef","tid":599458,"uid":114027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T12:18:35.000Z","msg":"小丑巴基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"971bca5c66137e5be51e0344f71459d319400ed8","tid":599458,"uid":42188,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T12:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/20/201919_b0e139d8eeb8432cc8b893fecab8102c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F20%2F201919_b0e139d8eeb8432cc8b893fecab8102c.png&h=1be719e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34a7cf48754b8e9297eb5ff189b0f599da797dc6","tid":599458,"uid":160414,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T12:20:48.000Z","msg":"綱手奶奶"},{"pid":"43b46dc12cc4cd4e0d3ee011fc8de57b269c193e","tid":599458,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34a7cf48754b8e9297eb5ff189b0f599da797dc6","tid":59